												<string>// Define the checkbox control and primary fill color control&#xD;var cwFlashCheckbox = thisComp.layer("Checkbox Controls").effect("CW Flash")("ADBE Checkbox Control-0001");&#xD;var primaryFillColorControl = myColor = thisProperty.value;&#xD;;&#xD;&#xD;// Define the original fill color value&#xD;var originalFillColor = text.animator("Color: Text Fill Color").property.fillColor&#xD;&#xD;// Check the status of the CW Flash checkbox&#xD;if (cwFlashCheckbox == 1) {&#xD;    primaryFillColorControl; // Inherit the color from the "Primary Fill Color" control&#xD;} else {&#xD;    originalFillColor; // Use the original fill color value&#xD;}&#xD;</string>
